                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-neon" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Treino de verdade</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-neon" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Atendimento com personal</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-check text-neon" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Artigos exclusivos</li>
                </ul>

                <a href="/auth/register?plan=free" class="btn btn-primary btn-full" style="font-weight: 800;">QUERO FAZER PARTE</a>
                <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #666; margin-top: 15px;">Depois, isso vira história pra contar.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="plan-card" style="background: #0f0f0f; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; opacity: 0.7;">
                <h2 style="color: white; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 5px;">Momentum Básico</h2>
                <span style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;">O começo do ritmo</span>
                
                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #222; padding: 20px 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <p style="color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem;">Para quem quer constância, clareza e direção.</p>
                </div>

                <ul style="text-align: left; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 30px; flex: 1; color: #666;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-circle" style="font-size: 6px; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle;"></i> Acesso à plataforma</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-circle" style="font-size: 6px; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle;"></i> Treinos estruturados</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><i class="fas fa-circle" style="font-size: 6px; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle;"></i> Acompanhamento básico</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.5;"><i class="fas fa-lock" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> IA de treinos (Futuro)</li>
